00:13:20.740 --> 00:13:23.320
But before I get
rolling, I wanted

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:26.440
to kick things off with some
audience participation-- get

00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:28.060
you guys energized, all right?

00:13:28.060 --> 00:13:31.570
And so just to provide
