00:13:31.570 --> 00:13:35.170
about a month or so ago, I was
looking at the latest results

00:13:35.170 --> 00:13:39.310
of the GDC State of the
Game Industry Survey

00:13:39.310 --> 00:13:41.830
among other things that
asked this question--

00:13:41.830 --> 00:13:45.010
which discovery methods,
you, the game developer,

