00:13:51.180 --> 00:13:55.060
of mouth, promotion on
the digital storefront--

00:13:55.060 --> 00:13:58.040
so that would be the
Play Store, for example--

00:13:58.040 --> 00:14:00.710
social media-- very popular--

00:14:00.710 --> 00:14:02.300
YouTube video--
which apparently is

00:14:02.300 --> 00:14:07.360
its own category-- and
traditional press and bloggers.

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:10.390
So take a second to let
this soak in, all right?

00:14:10.390 --> 00:14:11.345
Look at them closely.

00:14:11.345 --> 00:14:12.970
Keep them in your
mind, because they're

00:14:12.970 --> 00:14:15.460
