00:14:28.350 --> 00:14:30.580
So take a guess.

00:14:30.580 --> 00:14:33.140
What's the yellow bar
and what's the blue bar?

00:14:33.140 --> 00:14:33.640
All right.

00:14:33.640 --> 00:14:36.337
And I'll give you a second
to think about it, all right?

00:14:36.337 --> 00:14:37.170
Which is number one?

00:14:37.170 --> 00:14:39.520
And which is the last place one?

00:14:39.520 --> 00:14:40.260
OK.

00:14:40.260 --> 00:14:40.760
All right.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:43.940
So survey says that--

00:14:43.940 --> 00:14:46.860
you can imagine a drum roll--

00:14:46.860 --> 00:14:50.190
the number one choice
is social media.

00:14:50.190 --> 00:14:53.070
Very exciting, I know.

00:14:53.070 --> 00:14:55.740
And last place--
last place, survey

00:14:55.740 --> 00:15:01.190
says it was promotion on
the digital storefronts.

00:15:01.190 --> 00:15:05.000
And for completeness, this is
how everything else shook out.

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:07.520
So raise your hand
if you successfully

00:15:07.520 --> 00:15:11.142
guessed that social media
would be ranked first.

