design, and usability--

00:34:01.430 --> 00:34:03.350
positive performance signals.

00:34:07.530 --> 00:34:10.550
So what is the Android vitals
tool in the Play Console?

00:34:10.550 --> 00:34:15.739
It is a place where you can go
and see 15 performance metrics

00:34:15.739 --> 00:34:17.810
about your applications.

00:34:17.810 --> 00:34:20.750
These are broken out into
five performance areas--

00:34:20.750 --> 00:34:25.310
battery, stability, rendering,
startup time, and permission

00:34:25.310 --> 00:34:27.040
denials.

00:34:27.040 --> 00:34:29.170
For each of these metrics,
we provide you detailed

00:34:29.170 --> 00:34:35.929
reporting with breakdowns by
APK, OS version, and device.

00:34:35.929 --> 00:34:38.360
These help you to be able to
understand, where should you

00:34:38.360 --> 00:34:40.639
invest your time in improving
the tech and performance

00:34:40.639 --> 00:34:41.880
of your application?

00:34:41.880 --> 00:34:44.971
And these metrics are powered
by real users out there.

00:34:44.971 --> 00:34:46.429
The hundreds of
millions of Android

00:34:46.429 --> 00:34:49.360
users who've opted in to
sharing their data with Google,

00:34:49.360 --> 00:34:53.030
and you, our game partners.

00:34:53.030 --> 00:34:55.920
And these metrics are becoming
more and more important

00:34:55.920 --> 00:34:57.870
to the business success
of your application,

00:34:57.870 --> 00:35:01.900
because we can see that these
impact retention, engagement,

00:35:01.900 --> 00:35:03.390
and monetization
of games and apps.

00:35:07.557 --> 00:35:10.070
There's a lot of information
in Android vitals.

00:35:10.070 --> 00:35:12.760
So to help you prioritize
where you invest your time,

00:35:12.760 --> 00:35:14.940
at the top of the Android
vitals section you're

00:35:14.940 --> 00:35:16.630
provided core vitals.

00:35:16.630 --> 00:35:18.550
These are the four
metrics that we

00:35:18.550 --> 00:35:21.430
think are most
important to your users,

00:35:21.430 --> 00:35:24.310
and we have data to
show that they do impact

00:35:24.310 --> 00:35:26.270
your performance.

00:35:26.270 --> 00:35:29.540
And so the four metrics are in
