checking major metrics.

00:40:52.660 --> 00:40:54.700
So are we getting
major drops in reviews?

00:40:54.700 --> 00:40:56.980
Are we getting actual
spikes in reviews?

00:40:56.980 --> 00:40:58.990
And how we can
actually act on it.

00:40:58.990 --> 00:41:00.700
From a technical
perspective though, this

00:41:00.700 --> 00:41:02.980
is where our
developer and testing

00:41:02.980 --> 00:41:07.270
