00:43:54.900 --> 00:43:57.250
And more, in the end, quality.

00:43:57.250 --> 00:43:59.490
It's about discipline
and effectiveness.

00:43:59.490 --> 00:44:02.080
So know that every
single time that you're

00:44:02.080 --> 00:44:04.620
launching something, you have
to be monitoring actively.

00:44:04.620 --> 00:44:06.700
And once it's live, you
