00:58:13.980 --> 00:58:17.000
Prioritize testing of icons,
videos, and screenshots

00:58:17.000 --> 00:58:18.873
for the biggest impact.

00:58:18.873 --> 00:58:20.540
And you can also
invert your experiments

00:58:20.540 --> 00:58:24.670
to validate the true performance
before applying to all.

